{"tid":1728783,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"圍堵理工係為左測試18區開花","createTime":"2019-11-17T04:21:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T04:44:50.000Z","uid":81236,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8366407129e05d6ae1a6536c677244494aaf8ed9","tid":1728783,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:21:07.000Z","msg":"明白好多人覺得係圍魏救趙<br />\n<br />\n但當見到對方同藍絲同時清緊城大rb時<br />\n<br />\n就覺得係聲東擊西<br />\n<br />\n因為到而家進攻既力度好明顯唔係為左攻入，而係誘敵<br />\n<br />\n經過上次中大一役，所有人響應18區<br />\n<br />\n今日再攻再理大<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">各區都已經有部署</span><br />\n<br />\n各區勇武即時響應就變成被動<br />\n<br />\n所以請各位小心<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n各位可以化身和理非<br />\n<br />\n去理大附近做掩護"},{"pid":"91e238c90c28172e7a2cfc6bf7562578e9470cff","tid":1728783,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:21:48.000Z","msg":"****眾籌****<br />\n<br />\n唔好意思，仲係要借個位&amp;幫你推推POST<br />\n<br />\n鍾庭耀教授為今次運動發起了超大型全港性民調，長期追蹤今次運動大事件的民意 (eg. 721, 831) &amp; 證明香港人未放棄，然後做份國際文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 話比全世界聽：5毛網軍不代表香港人<br />\n(<span style=\"color: red;\">眾籌到而家先73%</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 仲要大家支持)<br />\n<br />\n第五期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1726268/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1726268/page/1</a> <span style=\"color: red;\">(new)</span><br />\n第三&amp;四期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1</a><br />\n第二期民調結果POST <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054</a><br />\n第一期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675545</a><br />\n<br />\n眾籌link:  <a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209&d=PiwLpsDni%2BEQUOLZDbBUzwomF%2BlBZ%2FxAFwVMru4Rc7Q%3D&h=1e30824f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209</a><br />\n官方link (我們香港人計劃) :<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pori.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pori.hk%2F&d=PiwLpsDni%2BEQUOLZDbBUzwomF%2BlBZ%2FxAFwVMru4Rc7Q%3D&h=502457da\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pori.hk/</a><br />\n<br />\n(對唔住，咁危難時刻下我知而家仲叫大家課金可能好反感，但我相信兄弟爬山，各有各做，行得通就全力去做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)"},{"pid":"8d424fa18de8b861a609b3c3e0a4c78d5ca89933","tid":1728783,"uid":182508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:22:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c1cfab9d39fd3f30dbd9e2e6bcdd0981b9790a55","tid":1728783,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:24:20.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1ec55852df780e21e35b176a56db799674985f87","tid":1728783,"uid":294,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:25:20.000Z","msg":"poly 根本得一隊狗, 係咁開槍<br />\n佢地根本唔係要入poly <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59a1a74dbb5370d119520881185f5a139246b9e8","tid":1728783,"uid":81236,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1ec55852df780e21e35b176a56db799674985f87","tid":1728783,"uid":294,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:25:20.000Z","msg":"poly 根本得一隊狗, 係咁開槍<br />\n佢地根本唔係要入poly <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:27:07.000Z","msg":"同當日攻中大好明顯係兩種武力<br />\n<br />\n但突然就成班約定幾人叫人出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"412a8237ee4aa031ac7cd491a7d33b4661e72899","tid":1728783,"uid":69334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:27:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6d04ea38b2efb6ff8338c8ccebaad7b05f7fe881","tid":1728783,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:28:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69b7b04c24a7881a46ea87506814b934bfaa11b5","tid":1728783,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:36:41.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0fb8c8b1659e88c32286a85c2affdde28e1174f0","tid":1728783,"uid":297230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:44:50.000Z","msg":"他們在打的是「<strong>中共政權保衛戰</strong>」，而你們僅僅是在打「<strong>香港生活方式保衛戰</strong>」<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1728140/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1728140/page/1</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>（一） Be Water(水聚散) 不能變為Be Castle（碉堡戰、陣地戰）</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">對付Be Water，第一就是分化，把勇武派、和理非派拆分，第二步是下餌，引誘勇武派進入「必守的陣地」，刺激他們建立碉堡，最好所有的勇武派都集中進入少數陣地（例如四所大學），然後隔絕、撒網、一舉成擒。</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>（二） 從「誰才是暴徒」辯論陷阱脫身</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">港人對抗港府還算旗鼓相當，畢竟兩邊都是被法治洗禮過的香港人，但是港人對付中共的無底綫宣傳統戰技能，坦白說，還是太嫩。世人關心香港事態的焦點從「港人要自由、要自治」，變成「人民和政府誰才是暴力方」的辯論，這正是北京要製造的焦點轉移。</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">（三） 一切回歸三個字 &ndash; 真普選</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">核心訴求只有一個：真普選，一切口號、行動、宣傳，都環繞真普選這單一訴求展開，這樣，世界聽得懂，連中國內地人民都聽得懂。</span>"}]}